The fundamental problem facing the company is encapsulated in that paragrap=
h:

* Intel doesn=E2=80=99t have the best manufacturing
* Intel doesn=E2=80=99t design the best chips
* Intel is out of the game in AI

Moreover, the future does not look bright; the problem with Intel=E2=80=99s=
 most recent earnings call was threefold:

* Intel=E2=80=99s is technically on pace to achieve the five nodes in four =
years Gelsinger promised (in truth two of those nodes were iterations), but=
